IMPORTANT REMINDERS
- Services must be received before the expiration date
- Services must be provided by the authorized provider
- This authorization does not guarantee payment; coverage is subject to eligibility and plan terms at the time of service
- Standard cost sharing (deductible, copay, coinsurance) still applies

