Welcome to Your Health Plan!

Dear {{member_name}},

Congratulations on your enrollment in {{plan_name}}! Your coverage is effective {{effective_date}}.

YOUR PLAN AT A GLANCE
Plan Type: {{plan_type}}
Member ID: {{member_id}}
Primary Care Provider: {{pcp_name}}
Annual Deductible: ${{deductible_individual}}
Out-of-Pocket Maximum: ${{oop_max_individual}}

GETTING STARTED
1. Your ID cards will arrive within 7-10 business days. In the meantime, you can access a digital ID card at www.healthplan.example.com
2. Schedule a wellness visit with your PCP — preventive care is covered at 100%
3. Download our mobile app to manage your benefits, find providers, and view claims
4. Register for the member portal at www.healthplan.example.com/register

NEED HELP?
Member Services: 1-800-555-PLAN (7526)
Available Monday-Friday, 8am-8pm ET
24/7 Nurse Line: 1-800-555-NURS

We're here to help you get the most from your benefits.

Sincerely,
Member Services Team

