Re: Appeal Received
Appeal Number: {{appeal_id}}
Member ID: {{member_id}}
Related Claim/Auth: {{claim_id}}{{auth_id}}

Dear {{member_name}},

We have received your appeal submitted on {{received_date}}.

NEXT STEPS
- Your appeal is under review by our clinical team
- You will receive a written decision by {{expected_decision_date}}
- If we need additional information, we will contact you
- You may submit additional supporting documentation at any time during the review

SUBMIT ADDITIONAL DOCUMENTS
Mail: Appeals Department, PO Box 12345, Processing Center, ST 00000
Fax: 1-800-555-FAX1
Secure Message: www.healthplan.example.com/messages

IMPORTANT
Your benefits continue during the appeal process. If this appeal involves an ongoing course of treatment, services will continue to be covered pending the appeal decision.

Questions? Call 1-800-555-PLAN and reference appeal number {{appeal_id}}.

Sincerely,
Appeals Department
